{"tid":1694750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚引玉］點解東方要散播fake news","createTime":"2019-11-05T09:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T09:41:33.000Z","uid":290205,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84ca9480332cf60764a713891d648cb64c26835a","tid":1694750,"uid":290205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"由何柱國做主席嘅東方係政府喉舌就係人都知，點解要突然傳出周同學準拔喉嘅消息？真係驚會民憤罷工？抑或傳一傳假消息，等周同學大步攬過之後手足有僥倖感覺然後放軟手腳？甚至乎係如果周同學真係咁不幸過身，手足嘅悲憤已經俾呢單假消息打散左少少？<br />\n<br />\n香港人而家要照顧嘅實在太多，其中一樣必須做嘅係睇對家點下棋，從而理解對家心態、弱點同死穴。咁先知道我地應該點行。<br />\n<br />\n我P牌一日得一個post想討論呢樣野，因為我覺得咁樣疑似流出假消息真係好詭異。以下開放討論。<br />\n<br />\n希望周同學大步「攬」過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足要頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b601fb9a90f590b5bc62023a2bac2c728c82d8","tid":1694750,"uid":50041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:30:19.000Z","msg":"何柱國係星島"},{"pid":"589fe7b6e6ddaaf07b8772426c75d55d267fde88","tid":1694750,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"東方 小罵大幫助是常識吧"},{"pid":"f25db34106b9f8b605bdf5185349c3c229805979","tid":1694750,"uid":60120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:31:19.000Z","msg":"何柱國係星島"},{"pid":"ff583a30fa74965a87490a359892923e9f633b81","tid":1694750,"uid":5303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40b601fb9a90f590b5bc62023a2bac2c728c82d8","tid":1694750,"uid":50041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:30:19.000Z","msg":"何柱國係星島"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:31:29.000Z","msg":"第一句已經錯得咁交關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed8e63df4982ca1293331082091b30e8994c34d","tid":1694750,"